    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I looked at your example and it seems that the attribute `value_features.Poids` hold `string` values rather than `number`. But [the widget only works with `number`](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/rangeSlider.html#requirements). You should update your values to match the widget expectation.",
